br />\nORG MODE 嚟"},{"pid":"69a43916eb8e6b988bc5ee2070db19d450ae1143","tid":454865,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無一隻掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你指乜嘢? 我剩係知所有Markdown parsers/editors都有一個死症: 一 export to PDF files, 所有internal links都一定fail晒; 但export to HTML files就乜樹都冇! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c05f9dd9797bc09819bc8abd2a6f4b27291181d","tid":454865,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見人用emacs唔錯，整table好快、但自己用開vim <br />\n(20m55s 開始​)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JWD1Fpdd4Pc?t=20m55s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJWD1Fpdd4Pc%3Ft%3D20m55s&d=sTAD1PYi3bk31fKjBgns7hxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=94572c4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JWD1Fpdd4Pc?t=20m55s</a></blockquote><br />\nORG MODE 嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nORG MODE係件好很強大嘅物體, 幾乎無所不能, 如果你用開emacs, 噉ORG MODE可以完全代替Markdown有突! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306b2c51cfbec07481972072840517d2afe74ce2","tid":454865,"uid":81716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"Gitbook editor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3148600fa21b086ffb13bc86391ebf5ba9d0f908","tid":454865,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gitbook editor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁! 呢隻係邊度彈出嚟? 橫跨三界(Windows, macOS, Linux)嘅 best markdown editors都冇推佢出嚟, 未聽過! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45be106ec1894d81d307121cd64cf2a600fe141","tid":454865,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:15:17.000Z","msg":"Latex <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他全部係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35776e622d32f846f8da5e8f58595d6aae3c8818","tid":454865,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Latex <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他全部係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用開始祖TeX, especially those control sequences(325 Primitives + 601 Macros) designed by my idol Donald Knuth! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nI don't like LaTeX, it's extremely difficult and troublesome to fine tune anything I need!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e374db31154108f1d25154b11c9a9e0db2e640ea","tid":454865,"uid":81716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Gitbook editor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁! 呢隻係邊度彈出嚟? 橫跨三界(Windows, macOS, Linux)嘅 best markdown editors都冇推佢出嚟, 未聽過! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實出左一段時間 裡面你所講既export PDF export HTML 都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而且仲能夠push 到gitbook 個網站到睇  現階段咁多隻中覺得最好 （free)<br />\n<br />\n我前個排諗住寫番d react js/native 教學up到gitbook 自己睇 先知道佢個MD做得咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c485c7723012f8fef71bb181100682644fa12a81","tid":454865,"uid":81716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:11:17.000Z","msg":"之所以無推到出黎 係因為好多best editor 網站 或者d人以為佢個software 剩係for push gitbook 用 點都估唔到佢可以唔login. 綁自己git server  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剩係睇d only for md 而睇少左佢 加上又少人講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bca56dee1ae2251ffb86674925a8c4ffc20b8d0","tid":454865,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之所以無推到出黎 係因為好多best editor 網站 或者d人以為佢個software 剩係for push gitbook 用 點都估唔到佢可以唔login. 綁自己git server  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剩係睇d only for md 而睇少左佢 加上又少人講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\noic. 等我得閒試下先! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac4035e377e72751359bd3e1deedb2996ee124c","tid":454865,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f006ab68c1faea164b45d67d4fbb6788be2b5035","tid":454865,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"呢兩日試裝/用咗個新node/Android app: <strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Joplin</span></span></strong> (<a href=\"http://joplin.cozic.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjoplin.cozic.net%2F&d=sTAD1PYi3bk31fKjBgns7hxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=88583d37\" target=\"_blank\">http://joplin.cozic.net/</a>), 係for note taking and to-do list用嘅.<br />\n<br />\n- notes係用markdown format, export出嚟都係md files.<br />\n- 暫時只可以sync去OneDrive.<br />\n- 佢個運作係vim-based, 所以如果你用慣vim, 會覺得好易用!<br />\n<br />\n係Android手機以markdown format記事, 多數人會用Writer Plus(易寫), 但Joplin個介面show markdown files時靚啲啲, 我覺得! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點裝?<br />\n<ins>Desktop Platforms:</ins><br />\nnpm -g install joplin / yarn global add joplin<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">Prerequisites</span>: <br />\n- You need to have node 8.x installed on Linux/Windows/macOS.<br />\n- Have to install both node packages &quot;node-gyp&quot; and &quot;sharp&quot; first.<br />\n- If on 32 bit old machine, you may have to manually compile the libvips library(<a href=\"https://github.com/jcupitt/libvips\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fjcupitt%2Flibvips&d=sTAD1PYi3bk31fKjBgns7hxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=fe1b6b8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/jcupitt/libvips</a>) from source before<br />\nbeing able to install &quot;sharp&quot; above.)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>Android Platform:</ins><br />\nJust search keyword &quot;joplin&quot; and install.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>P.S. 呢個app好似好新, 冇乜download statistics. 原作者好似係reddit推介過, 但啲人好似連登仔噉, 十個有九個潑冷水, 尤其嗰啲emacs死忠, 哈!)</em><br />\n<br />\n<em>P.S. 我係喺部XP裏面個Ubuntu 14.04 VM(No GUI, just Terminal)裝嘅, 搞咗兩晚先裝到, 因為部機係32 bit nettop(Intel ATOM 330), 要manually compile libvips library先成功裝到sharp後先可以裝到joplin! </em>"},{"pid":"083cd8778124e5511dd7284b7461e2178ed1727f","tid":454865,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無一隻掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你指乜嘢? 我剩係知所有Markdown parsers/editors都有一個死症: 一 export to PDF files, 所有internal links都一定fail晒; 但export to HTML files就乜樹都冇! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有wysiwyg既無preview<br />\n有preview既wysiwyg<br />\n<br />\n到頭來好似真係得Github嗰個最好<br />\n呢期諗會唔會自己寫個出嚟無咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過要得閒先"},{"pid":"9c6aa3cdd6dc542609930fc2dd7788f76b5b7b93","tid":454865,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gitbook editor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個望落幾好"},{"pid":"5be264c77ad5fd263d7f67289018aab42a8dc3d8","tid":454865,"uid":90331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:00:39.000Z","msg":"typora<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://typora.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftypora.io&d=sTAD1PYi3bk31fKjBgns7hxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=cd68ee8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://typora.io</a>"},{"pid":"941e4d11342ffc3f5b87db938634de0ce1d284c1","tid":454865,"uid":36738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>typora<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://typora.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftypora.io&d=sTAD1PYi3bk31fKjBgns7hxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=cd68ee8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://typora.io</a></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我都係用緊呢個 <br />\n勁多language syntax highlight support, 又唔洗死記md d syntax, 仲要WYSIWYG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d450c8db451a5df97a7e95af8cc351512c704e67","tid":454865,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>typora<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://typora.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftypora.io&d=sTAD1PYi3bk31fKjBgns7hxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=cd68ee8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://typora.io</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隻我部32bit低能機裝唔到! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}